    <string name="faq_10_body">Yes. Using good quality earphones will give a much better hearing experience and improved sound clarity.</string>
    <string name="faq_10_title">Do earphones affect performance?</string>
    <string name="faq_11_body">For best results:\n\nUse good quality earphones.\n\nPlace your phone near the audio source (e.g., near the TV or speaker)\n\nUse personalized audio profiles</string>
    <string name="faq_11_title">How can I get the best hearing experience?</string>
    <string name="faq_12_body">Anyone who wants better sound clarity or mild hearing support in daily life.</string>
    <string name="faq_12_title">Who should use SunoX?</string>
    <string name="faq_1_body">SunoX is a hearing assistance app that enhances sound clarity using personalized audio settings.</string>
    <string name="faq_1_title">What is SunoX?</string>
    <string name="faq_2_body">No. SunoX is not a medical device and does not replace professional hearing aids. It is designed for general hearing support.</string>
    <string name="faq_2_title">Is SunoX a medical hearing aid?</string>
    <string name="faq_3_body">Yes. SunoX offers a 7-day free trial. After that, you can subscribe for ₹99.</string>
    <string name="faq_3_title">Is the app free?</string>
    <string name="faq_4_body">After 7 days, a ₹99 subscription is required to continue using premium features.</string>
    <string name="faq_4_title">What happens after the trial ends?</string>
    <string name="faq_5_body">Yes. All future upgrades and updates are free after subscription.</string>
    <string name="faq_5_title">Are future updates free?</string>
    <string name="faq_6_body">It\'s a quick in-app hearing test that helps personalize your audio settings.</string>
    <string name="faq_6_title">What is the audiogram test?</string>
    <string name="faq_7_body">The test takes about 7–8 minutes.</string>
    <string name="faq_7_title">How long does the audiogram test take?</string>
    <string name="faq_8_body">It\'s recommended for the best experience, as it helps tailor the sound to your hearing needs.</string>
    <string name="faq_8_title">Do I need to take the audiogram test?</string>
    <string name="faq_9_body">Audio profiles let you save and switch between customized sound settings for different environments.</string>
    <string name="faq_9_title">What are audio profiles?</string>
